column7: A Rare find in Southlake! Calais Custom Homes presents a stunning One Acre homesite. This Summer friendly, East facing backyard with gorgeous mature trees is ready for you to create the home of your dreams!!!! Nestled in a quiet neighborhood with NO HOA, this building lot is a great canvas to bring your vision to life. Calais Custom Homes, a long-time, premiere and highly-respected area builder offers you endless possibilities to build to your needs. Mockingbird Lane has access to Southlake Town Square and offers easy commuting to Dallas, Fort Worth and the DFW Airport One acre site - 100 feet wide and approximately 435 feet deep Fully wooded homesite in an established Southlake neighborhood No HOA. Flexibility to build any design style with Calais Custom Homes East backyard that opens to a Creek at the far back-side of the property Quiet end of cul-de-sac location with no traffic; Very private! Carroll ISD location and fully within the City of Southlake

column7: Beautiful, single story with no interior elevation changes - truly one level! Mostly wood floors, current paint tones & modern flair thru-out! Open & light w-quality trim package & ceiling treatments. 4 BRs + large flex-game room (OR 5th BR) in a desirable 3-way split - lots of privacy for everyone! Spacious study w-French doors & bright white shiplap walls. Oversized family rm is open to the enormous kitchen-nook w- huge granite island & tons of white cabinetry cabinetry to the ceiling, dbl ovens, gas range, pot-filler & W-I pantry! Lovely formal dining space w-adjacent butlery w-wine cooler! Lux primary suite w-huge closet & gorgeous bath-exquisite tile detail & quartz vanities! Secondary BR's feature ensuite baths & W-I closets. You'll love the large, enclosed patio with fireplace for 4 season enjoyment! Plenty of room to build a pool. 3 garage spaces! Other features:2 tankless water heaters, lightning rods added by seller. Served by exemplary Carroll ISD!

column7: Beautiful hard to find single story built by Heritage Custom Homes. Saddleback Ridge Estates offers private gated 1 acre lots with mature trees, ponds and wildlife all around. This Texas Vernacular style home offers the perfect combination of contemporary touches, with modern materials. This luxurious residence features high ceilings, natural stones, and beautiful millwork throughout. Flooded with natural light, the open floor plan seamlessly connects the elegant living room, gourmet kitchen, and dining area. Private owners retreat, spacious spa-like bathroom with soaking tub and oversized custom walk in closet. All guest bedrooms have full ensuite baths. Beautiful executive study off main living space with wall of glass. Large game room perfect for entertaining with sliding door to outdoor covered patio. Chef's Kitchen with stainless steel appliances including professional grade 48 in gas range, 60 in Thermador refrigerator freezer and wine fridge, prep kitchen with sink, ice maker and second dishwasher. Separate guest house with bedroom, kitchen, living and attached 1 car garage. Custom heated pool designed and built by Leschber Designs. Completion Date of Spring 2025.

column7: Nestled in the prestigious and gated Saddleback Ridge Estates, this brand-new contemporary home exemplifies modern luxury. Built by JPK Builders and designed in collaboration with Lindbergh Designs of Architecture, this exceptional residence offers 5 bedrooms, 5 full bathrooms, and 3 half baths, all situated on over an acre of beautifully landscaped land. The open-concept layout is perfect for both entertaining and everyday living, with standout features like a custom glass-enclosed wine lounge, a study, an entertainment room with a bar, a media room, and a versatile flex room. The chefs kitchen is a dream, featuring top-of-the-line Miele appliances, stunning quartzite countertops, and an oversized island, plus a separate catering kitchen complete with its own dishwasher and oven. The luxurious primary retreat offers a spa-like bath with a walk-in shower and a freestanding bathtub. Step outside to an expansive outdoor oasis, complete with a covered patio and a fully equipped outdoor kitchen. Nearby Grapevine Lake and Bob Jones Park! Northwest ISD or Open Enrollment by application process to Carroll ISD!

column7: This modern-contemporary home is situated on a .72 acre lot in the heart of Southlake and offers unparalleled luxury and comfort. The exterior features stucco and stone construction with a front courtyard and was completed by Calais Homes in 2023. Enjoy nearby Bicentennial Park. Crescent Heights is one of the newest gated communities. The home is 9639 sq feet per appraisal, plus 600 sq feet of private patio space. This luxurious home boasts 6 oversized bedrooms, 6 full baths, 2 half baths, 5 living areas, 2 dining areas, an exercise room, sauna, study, game room, media room, 2nd-floor coffee bar with kitchenette and a 4-car garage. A floating staircase greets you at entry and flows into the formal living and dining area with 25-foot ceilings, glass railings, 2 designer chandeliers. The primary ensuite plus three large secondary bedrooms are located on level 2. Two guest bedrooms are located on level 1. The kitchen is equipped with 2 Miele dishwashers, double ovens, a steamer, warmer, Gaganeau (German) cooking modules, 2 sinks, paneled Sub Zero and abundant custom cabinetry. Exterior features include an outdoor living and dining area with remote control shades, a 36-inch gas grill, sink and 2 large gas burners. The firepit is adjacent to the outdoor living. Amenities include glass railings, glass door elevator, Pella windows, Lutron automation, 5-inch select white oak flooring in bedrooms, closet and study, designer porcelain tile in living and kitchen.Designer quartzite counters are featured throughout the home with a waterfall design in the kitchen and bar. Ocean Blue and White Mustang quartzite are the selections. Other features include a well for lawn and garden and foam-encapsulated insulation.Dont miss the shampoo sink and chair. Exemplary Carroll ISD. Designed with meticulous attention to detail. See a list of amenities on NTREIS. Agent to meet and requires 24 to 48 notice to show. call for exceptions.Proof of funds statement or letter from the lender.

Step inside to an open, light-filled floor plan featuring wall-to-wall windows that flood the kitchen and living room with natural light. The heart of the home showcases updated appliances, designer light fixtures, hardwood floors, and stylish hardware that create a cohesive, sophisticated look. Architectural details like elegant wainscoting, plantation shutters, and custom built-ins add character throughout. Upstairs, youll find a spacious game roomideal for entertaining or relaxing. Step outside to your private backyard retreat, complete with a sparkling pool and spa combo. This stunning home is move-in ready, offering the perfect blend of modern updates and classic charm in Southlake, Texas.

column7: Welcome to your dream home in the highly sought-after South Ridge Lakes neighborhood! This exceptional 4-bedroom, 1.5-story residence, complete with a dedicated office, offers a perfect blend of modern updates, versatile spaces, and unparalleled convenience. Step into the spacious office, an ideal setting for working from home, featuring a stunning wall of windows that provide a picturesque view of the lush professionally designed backyard. Whether you're tackling daily tasks or seeking inspiration, this space is designed to enhance productivity and comfort. The living room and kitchen with Quartzite counter tops, gas cook top and hardwood floors are the heart of the home. A welcoming space to entertain friends and family. Unwind on the serene covered patio, a tranquil retreat perfect for relaxing after a long day. The expansive backyard offers endless possibilities, whether you envision a vibrant garden, a playground, or even adding a sparkling pool to enjoy during warm summer days. The extended laundry room is a multifunctional space, perfect for laundry, crafts, or exercise, complete with an entire wall of added storage to keep everything organized and within reach. The fourth bedroom, located upstairs with a full bathroom, offers flexibility to serve as a game room or guest suite, catering to your unique needs. Notable updates include all windows replaced in 2016 and 2019, and a Class 4 hail resistant roof replaced in 2019, ensuring peace of mind and energy efficiency. This remarkable home is a true gem, offering a lifestyle of comfort, convenience, and endless possibilities. Don't miss the chance to make it yours!

column7: REMODELED custom home in Southlakes Oak Pointe blends warmth with a touch of elegance. Each formal space offers a unique elementthe study has herringbone wood floors-the formal living room overlooks the rock garden with two story view of the green space and a newly installed 46-inch gas fireplace box with quartzite slab surround and the dining room offers a coffered ceiling. The first-floor primary suite offers a vaulted ceiling with a wall of windows overlooking the backyard, while the remodeled bath features heated marble floors, a seamless glass shower with dual heads, a rain shower, and a handheld as well as mosaic marble backsplashes and a soaker tub. A first-floor guest suite with a spa-like en-suite bath overlooks the pool. The hardwood floors carry up the stairs and thru the hallway to the game room with wet bar. Double pocket doors open to the carpeted media room. Three bedrooms each feature remodeled en-suite baths-two with showers and one with a deep tub-plus spacious walk-in closets. The backyard is lovely with a sparkling play pool, spa, wood-burning fireplace, arbor-shaded seating, built-in grill, and ample space to play. A gated drive leads to a 4-car garage, while updated HVAC, roof, and water heaters ensure peace of mind. This exceptional, move-in ready home is a rare find in Southlakeand walking distance to parks!

column7: Nestled on a serene, spacious corner lot of over an acre, this inviting family home offers a tranquil escape surrounded by mature trees and a charming circular driveway. Located just minutes from Southlakes premier dining, shopping, and with convenient access to Hwy 114, this property blends privacy with accessibility. The heart of the home is the kitchen, featuring stainless steel appliances and granite countertops, perfect for both everyday living and entertaining. The main floor boasts a luxurious primary suite with a view of the pool and the lush backyard. Upstairs, each bedroom has its own private access to the balcony, creating a unique indoor-outdoor flow. The expansive patio deck and pool area set the scene for memorable gatherings or peaceful evenings, where you can unwind with unobstructed views. With plenty of space to make it your own, this property promises both comfort and room to grow. Updates include: New electrical panel w LED lighting throughout entire home, Interior & Exterior paint, New plumbing for all bathrooms & kitchen, all 4 Full bathrooms completely renovated, Kitchen completely renovated, Primary Bedroom removed all sheetrock and raised ceiling, New Luxury Vinyl flooring throughout entire home, All new windows, New doors except two back exterior doors, New plaster and equipment for the pool, New fence.

This luxury home in the desirable Ridgeview community is just minutes from Southlake Town Square. From the moment you enter, you'll appreciate the meticulous attention to detail & finishes, including plantation shutters, hardwood floors, granite counters, an ice machine, two laundry rooms, surround sound speakers, and smart home features at your fingertips. The main level features a mother-in-law suite and a primary suite that offers the comfort of a spa-like retreat bathroom and spacious walk-in closets. The kitchen, open to the family room, is equipped with double ovens, gas cooktop, built-in microwave, huge island, a coffee station area, and ample storage. The family room boasts high ceilings, an abundance of natural light, a stone-surround gas fireplace, and views of the pool area. A butlers pantry off the family and dining rooms includes an ice machine and sink. Also on the main level is a private office complete with built ins. Upstairs, you'll discover three spacious bedrooms that offer both comfort and functionality, along with a huge game room perfect for family fun or entertaining friends. For added convenience, a second laundry room makes chores a breeze! Two of the bedrooms share a beautifully designed Jack and Jill bathroom, with customized closets providing extra storage space. The third bedroom is a private retreat, complete with its own full bathroom. This layout is perfect for families or guests, ensuring everyone has their own space while enjoying the best of modern living! The stunning backyard space, thoughtfully added in 2021, boasts a luxurious pool and spa, perfect for relaxing or entertaining. Enjoy the elegant travertine decking, enhanced by beautiful lighting and outdoor speakers that set the mood for any gathering. The convenience of a full bathroom adds a touch of luxury, while the privacy fence ensures a tranquil retreat. Plus, the additional covered patio area is ideal for outdoor dining and lounging.

The primary bedroom is bright and spacious, with a fabulous en suite featuring dual vanities, a frameless glass & tile shower with rainhead, and a luxurious soaking tub. Out back, find even more space to relax and entertain with an expansive covered patio and fireplace. Enjoy easy access to Highways 121 and 114 as well as ample shopping, dining, and entertainment at the ever popular Main Street in downtown Grapevine and Grapevine Mills Mall as well as opportunities for camping, boating, fishing, & more at Grapevine Lake. This is a must see!!!

column7: Charming Creekwood Estates Home with Modern Rustic Appeal! Nestled in the highly sought-after neighborhood of Creekwood Estates within the renowned GCISD. Commuting is made easy with the train station a short distance away in beautiful downtown Grapevine. Imagine your next chapter unfolding in this picturesque setting on Creekwood Drive.

Location, location, location! Nestled just one street from Main St, this beautifully renovated 3-bedroom, 2-bath home is a stone's throw from the festive charm of Grapevine, the Christmas Capital of Texas. Step inside to find a perfect blend of modern comfort and mid-century charm. The fully fenced backyard, complete with two doggie doors, is a pup paradiseperfect for your furry friends to roam free. Need extra space? And lets not forget the garage, boasting remarkable storage and shelving, plus an automated staircase thats just as cool as it sounds. This home is bursting with character and charm, located in an up-and-coming neighborhood! Old homes are being gutted and remodeled, or leveled for the next million-dollar dream home. Dont miss your chance to make this mid-century gem your ownschedule a tour today and step into a lifestyle thats as vibrant as Grapevine itself!

column7: Spacious 2 story home in GCISD, centrally located and on a quiet circle! Neutral colors provide a blank slate - ready for your personal preferences. Oversize rooms throughout - you'll find a large living and dining room as you enter the home. Kitchen is open to the breakfast and family rooms with FP and it overlooks the shady backyard. There's a deep soaking tub + walk in shower plus double vanities for a relaxing spa experience every day. Large trees for shade both front and back and an oversize covered porch with gas hookup for grill. Roof replaced 2022, water heater replaced 9-2024. Carpet upstairs and in family room replaced 9-2024. Fogged window panes scheduled for replacement this month. Storage shed in side yard for yard toys and tools. Only 2 blocks to Grapevine Elementary!

column7: NEW ROOF Beautifully updated one story home nestled in the peaceful Woods Community of Grapevine and within the highly acclaimed GCISD. The kitchen showcases sleek granite countertops, a convenient breakfast bar, updated white cabinetry with stylish glass inserts, and chic stone backsplash. Step outside to enjoy a cozy wooden deck, perfect for relaxing or entertaining, overlooking the expansive backyard with mature landscaping. Ideally located, this home is just minutes from Grapevine Lake, the charming historic Main Street, and a short drive from DFW Airport.

column7: Fully Remodeled One Story Duplex in Historic Grapevine! Prime Location just blocks from Downtown Grapevine & Lake Grapevine. 2 Bedrooms, 2 Full Baths in each side of Duplex. Potential Investment Opportunity...Lease, Air Bnb, Occupy One Side & Lease the Other Side, Put the Inlaws in the Other Side, or Better Yet...Convert to a 4 Bedroom, 4 Full Bath Home for Multi Generational Living. Driveway to back of property w 2 Car Garage, 2 Car Carport & Spacious Yard w Plenty of Room to Roam & Play or Entertain. Within Minutes of DFW Airport, Gaylord Texan, Shopping, Dining Entertainment & All the Quaint Events that Grapevine hosts. Dont Miss This Rare Opportunity in a Sought After Location!

Welcome to this move-in ready condo offering the perfect blend of convenience and low-maintenance living. Located in the vibrant heart of Grapevine, this two-story home features an inviting layout. The oversized primary bedroom upstairs boasts a private balcony, ensuite bath, and a spacious walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms on the second floor share a full bath, making it ideal for families or guests. Enjoy the ease of a dedicated full-sized laundry room, with a half bath conveniently located on the first floor. Step outside to your private courtyard, perfect for relaxing or entertaining, with direct access to a two-car garage that includes a large secure outdoor storage closet. This home is within walking distance of a nearby elementary school and scenic lake trails, ideal for outdoor enthusiasts. With HOA covering exterior maintenance and yard care, youll enjoy more free time to take advantage of the community clubhouse and pool. Conveniently located close to Grapevines best shopping, dining, Grapevine Lake, and DFW Airport, this condo truly has it all!

column7: So much space in this large 5 bedroom home in north Grapevine in Carroll ISD! Beautiful curb appeal and mature trees in front. Fantastic layout. column7: Welcome to the Millican House, a one-of-a-kind luxury home in the Historic District, walking distance from Main Street. Originally built in 1935 as a Sears kit house, this property has been carefully preserved and rebuilt into an approximately 3, 935 square foot masterpiece. The current homeowners have thoughtfully preserved portions of the original house, adding to the charm and character of this stunning home. This property boasts four bedrooms and four bathrooms, providing ample space for comfortable living. The primary bedroom, study and an open floor plan built for entertaining are all conveniently located on the first floor. The guest house features a living area, bathroom and bedroom, perfect for hosting guests or as a private retreat. Venture outside and enjoy the refreshing cocktail pool, outdoor kitchen and living center, surrounded by plenty of lawn space for play. column7: Welcome to the GE Hurst Historical House originally built in 1910. This home was extensively renovated and added on to in 2018 and is the essence of Grapevine historic living. It is situated on .54 acres with many native trees and a 960 sq ft garage workshop that has the look of an original barn. The house has over 4560 sq ft under roof and 2780 sq ft of living space. Many of the original features and trim work were preserved while fully updating the complete house and structure with all the modern top amenities. The renovated structure was rebuilt on top of a steel pier and beam foundation. The primary bedroom and guest suit along with the primary living areas are all located downstairs, while the upstairs has two additional bedrooms with full baths, a living area, and unique spacious office. The home has a porte-cochere near the mud room and laundry for easy entrance. Seller is a relative of listing agent.
